{"tid":1087613,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"我想用7頭嚟整figure公仔！","createTime":"2019-04-01T12:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T11:07:37.000Z","uid":154793,"like":2004,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"e44f7bf85275adb83aeeaacd7ab2f4fe151c45ed","tid":1087613,"uid":154793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"話說7年前我擺檔畫畫<br />\n有人出題比我畫咗個7頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFeyxZz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFeyxZz.png&h=b0051f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家正值7年之癢，<br />\n我想用佢嚟出figure公仔！<br />\n<br />\n一開始我求其搵咗間廠整，<br />\n叫佢幫我做得3D啲Detail啲寫實啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jLRUhss.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjLRUhss.png&h=a1965936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果出現咗樓下呢隻孽種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4H4EGe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4H4EGe.png&h=ee68df1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJa58At.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJa58At.png&h=56b1f24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到佢即刻有一股衝動<br />\n好想即刻燒佢落去陪太公太嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我嘅figure夢並沒有輕言放棄，<br />\n為咗加強文青嘅感覺同宣揚環保嘅訊息，<br />\n我嘗試加入大自然嘅元素落個7頭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmcz1Yg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmcz1Yg.png&h=2ef11c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGLBvRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGLBvRA.png&h=1a5558de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nR4KEKU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnR4KEKU.png&h=dd67db19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到佢地即刻有一股衝動<br />\n好想即刻種佢地落田到種生機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我都係決定換第二間廠整7頭figure<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtrQAkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtrQAkW.png&h=400c1309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未完待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec30c055de1f8620796e6c4d196a0e21501b17ad","tid":1087613,"uid":29080,"like":132,"dislike":1,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"成碌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99896c8c994b3872c40b7fa859694e5e808cc46c","tid":1087613,"uid":12264,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"笑到我噴左啖飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi